Notes on the Shared Library Symbols:
The 'no-symbols-control-file' lintian tag is intentionally ignored for
version 0.0.21. We are waiting for the C++ API to "burn in" and stabilise
before generating the master symbols control file.

Plan: Generate via 'dpkg-gensymbols' once we hit v0.1.0.

    dpkg-gensymbols -plibwk2gtkpdf0 > debian/libwk2gtkpdf0.symbols
